What you need to know:

In September last year, BK witnessed a new dawn when it acquired its first modern competition and training mats courtesy of NOC-K. It’s at this function presided over by Tergat  at Aryan Samaj Sports Hall, Parklands, Nairobi, that  Muchiri and Shigoli shook hands, vowing to end the wrangles that had ruined the growth of the sport.That seems not to have worked.  